This Phase 3 study is intended to assess the efficacy of the Quadrivalent VLP Influenza Vaccine during the 2017-2018 influenza season in healthy adults 18 to 64 years of age.

 One dose of Quadrivalent Virus-Like Particles (VLP) Influenza Vaccine (30 1/2g/strain) or of placebo will be administered to approximately 10,000 subjects.

